    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Building on topchef's answer,</p>\n\n<p>For 2.0.31-beta I had to use Mockito.anyVararg instead of Matchers.anyVararrg:</p>\n\n<pre><code>when(a.b(anyInt(), anyInt(), Mockito.&lt;String&gt;anyVararg())).thenReturn(b);\n</code></pre>\n"
